ds, cover floor consoles, HCV covers, and panel and box rear floor consoles, as well as ash boxes, front box floor consoles, foot rests, panel instrument clusters, AC vents, and glove box assembly products for four wheelers. It also provides leg shields, cover frames, engine cooling duct housings, and panel side covers for two wheelers; side covers, tool boxes, grill fronts, and corner vanes for commercial vehicles; and moulds and dies. Machino Plastics Limited was incorporated in 1986 and is based in Gurugram, India."}}